title: Cinema Secrets Ultimate Foundation Palette, #03
description: Perfect for skin with olive and yellow undertones, this multi-purpose palette of five highly pigmented foundations can be used to highlight, shade and contour, and create a custom foundation. Spreads smoothly, provides full coverage with sheer application, and ensures a soft, natural finish. Clear acrylic case snaps closed and is compact enough to stash in any bag. (Cinema Secrets colors 301-63A, 302-65A, 303-66A, 201-67, 202-20.)

title: Neutrogena Shine Control Primer, 1 Ounce
description: Lightweight, nongreasy formula with patentpending rice protein technology acts like a sponge to absorb excess oil so skin stays shinefree and fresh looking all day. Helps makeup apply more smoothly and last longer. Optical modifiers help minimize the look of pores

title: Bdellium Tools Professional Antibacterial Makeup Brush Studio Line - Flat Eye Definer 714
description: This brush is for eye definition and shadow lining with precision resulting in a professional look. The straight edged tip allows for a smooth with your liner or eye shadow. Bdellium Tools Studio Line of brushes are makeup tools designed from top grade materials and assembled by hand for a superior quality. Each and every brush showcases the flawless application medium that is Bdellium Tools. From precisely shaped brush heads to balanced mixtures of natural and/or synthetic hair bristles, the luxuriously lacquered long wooden handle of the Studio Line will give you optimum control and comfort resulting in a perfect application time after time. All of the Studio Line brushes are treated with an antibacterial agent on the bristles.

title: Got2b Powder'ful Volumizing Styling Powder, 0.35 Ounce
description: Take your volume to new heights with Got2b powerful volumizing styling powder. This is the latest cool find to instantly volumize your hair. And guess what, it's a powder. What Got2b volumizing styling powder does is so cool, you have never seen anything like it. It's so easy to have amazing volume in an instant with no tools needed. The revolutionary weightless formula texturizes each hair strand to create maximum volume in an instant.

description: Get Flawless, Shine-Free Skin Instantly And On-The-Go With Makeup Tailor Made For Your Skin.
